metadata.name: High seas - SFlights I
metadata.description:
Immersed in the fury of the ocean, our dreams will come out stronger.

Distant oceans, where only our dreams dare; and they do it like wings, sometimes flowing with the sea and sometimes fighting it.

"Sea Flights" is a collection of digital compositions based on photo manipulation + vector figures that give identity to each piece.
Each piece consists of a meticulous work to resignify each element that composes it.
